data.description: OMG , Stop the car and stop your searching. Home just reduced Almost $100K. Due to family issues Owner must sell which once was his retirement castle. This home has been modified and remodeled for the potential new owners that want a hassle free home with NO HOA fees what so ever. This corner lot is a family gatherings dream. Real pretty back yard and friendly neighbors hi. The interior and exterior have been freshly painted, and new front and back doors have been installed. Additionally, the home boasts a new AC unit, roof, and stainless steel appliances. With brick all around and a complete new fence, this home offers both style and security. Its prime location allows for easy access to various parts of Houston, with a 3-minute drive to US 290, 5 minutes to I-10/Katy freeway, easy commute to either airport. If you appreciate the finer things in life, don't miss the opportunity to view this property. Contact me for more information. Home has never flooded..NO HOA ! Big savings.
